# HTTP API contracts (blocking)

Finish only when ALL apply:

1. **`docs/API_CHANGELOG.md`** — extend **`[Unreleased]`** (routes, limits, error **`code`** s, SPA parity impacts).
2. **`npm run docs:registry`** — regenerates inventories + **`docs/generated/API_GENERATION_CATALOG.md`**.
3. If partners read **`openapi`**, update **`docs/openapi/v1.openapi.yaml`** same branch.
4. If ModelClone-X / enhance behavior changed, sync **`docs/API_GENERATION_UX_PARITY.md`**.

Run **`npm run verify:api-changelog`** before hand-off (**`SKIP_API_CHANGELOG_VERIFY=1`** escape hatch).
